snippet.title: Journey to Foundation - Release Date Trailer | PS VR2 Games
snippet.description:
In Journey to Foundation, you play as Agent Ward, a spy with the Commission of Public Safety.

The future is in your hands. In this immersive roleplaying adventure, you decide who will rise and what is lost to the fires of anarchy. 

Disguise, hack, and blast your way through Asimov's groundbreaking sci-fi universe using the most advanced tools the Galactic Empire has to offer.

Where will your journey lead you? Find out on October 26, 2023.

#ps5 #psvr2 #psvr2games #scifi #asimov #foundation
